text: Valea Vinului may refer to the following places in Romania: * Valea Vinului, a commune of Satu Mare County * Valea Vinului, a village in the commune Rodna, Bistrița-Năsăud County * Valea Vinului, a tributary of the Cormaia in Bistrița-Năsăud County * Valea Vinului (Someș), a tributary of the Someș in Satu Mare County * Valea Vinului, a tributary of the Taița in Tulcea County * Valea Vinului (Vișeu), a tributary of the Vișeu in Maramureș County * Valea Vinului, another name for the river Pârâul Vinului in Harghita County ==See also== *Valea (disambiguation) *Vinu (name)
title: Valea Vinului (disambiguation)
